in perpetuating America.

15:45.708 --> 15:47.415
-[laughs]
-[Steph] Stop.

15:48.750 --> 15:50.250
[applause]

15:52.625 --> 15:56.583
Good evening and welcome
to the proud denizens

15:56.665 --> 15:58.040
of Vault 32.

15:58.125 --> 15:59.625
[applause]

16:05.291 --> 16:08.833
We are bonded

16:08.916 --> 16:11.166
not just as neighbors

16:11.250 --> 16:13.791
but by a shared duty.

16:13.875 --> 16:16.708
To keep the candle of civilization lit.

16:17.750 --> 16:19.666
While the rest of the world has been cast

16:19.750 --> 16:21.750
into darkness.

16:22.958 --> 16:24.416
Soon,

16:24.500 --> 16:27.250
if our measurements are correct,

16:27.333 --> 16:31.583
radiation levels on the surface
are dropping fast enough

16:31.666 --> 16:35.625
that the next generation,
Lucy and Monty's children,

16:35.708 --> 16:38.083
will be able to recolonize.

16:38.165 --> 16:40.208
-[laughs]
-[applause]

16:40.290 --> 16:42.665
-Whoo!
-[cheering]

16:42.750 --> 16:45.500
[Hank] Yes.

16:47.915 --> 16:49.665
After 200 years...

16:50.708 --> 16:53.708
...we don't know much
about what's up there.

16:53.790 --> 16:56.790
Desperation, violence,

16:56.875 --> 16:58.750
lawlessness.

16:58.833 --> 17:01.916
These survivors will need to be shown

17:02.000 --> 17:03.833
a better way.

17:03.916 --> 17:07.500
I'll admit I'm sometimes afraid

17:07.583 --> 17:11.583
that mean old world
will change us instead.

17:11.665 --> 17:14.165
But then I look at my daughter...

17:14.250 --> 17:15.750
[chuckles]

17:15.833 --> 17:18.708
[Hank] ...who's such a beautiful bride,
and her new husband.

17:18.790 --> 17:22.040
And I am not afraid.

17:22.125 --> 17:25.915
I feel hope.

17:27.250 --> 17:28.875
To Lucy MacLean.

17:28.958 --> 17:30.291
-And to this marriage.
-[applause]

17:30.375 --> 17:32.125
And to hope.

17:32.208 --> 17:34.625
[cheering]

17:34.708 --> 17:36.958
Let's dance. [laughs] Hit it.

