18:59.833 --> 19:01.125
[door whooshes]

19:05.916 --> 19:08.583
Ah, isn't it great?

19:08.666 --> 19:10.625
Every big moment of our lives

19:10.708 --> 19:12.916
is gonna happen right here.

19:14.333 --> 19:17.416
Picture the Christmas mornings
around the tree.

19:17.500 --> 19:20.000
We have everything

19:20.083 --> 19:22.083
with the hand-me-downs;
an icebox, a blender.

19:22.166 --> 19:23.750
-They-they even gave us...
-[clothes hitting floor]

19:27.250 --> 19:28.375
Huh.

19:31.916 --> 19:33.250
Okey dokey.

